For any doubters out there:

THIS version (DVN) is only a demo! You can install it and play for many hours before you discover that the game puts an halt to your advances in February (in game February of course). I was just about to advance to Elitserien when i found this out and now i NEED the game (I'm addicted).

Oh... And when you install it asks if you want to overwrite a file or not. It seems that they included the executable packager file both in the archive as well as bundled with the archive. If you choose no the installation aborts the process and thus you can't play the game. Choose yes and it will work.

Correction!

Do NOT overwrite the file and it should work :P. Sorry.
